<div><span style="display:inline-block; width:1.5em; height:1.5em; margin:1px 0; border:1px solid black; background-color:#D172A2; color:black; font-size:100%; text-align:center;">&#160;</span>&#160;7. <a href="/wiki/Tver" title="Tver">Tver</a> dialect</div>
Southern dialects
<div><span style="display:inline-block; width:1.5em; height:1.5em; margin:1px 0; border:1px solid black; background-color:#FF9B06; color:black; font-size:100%; text-align:center;">&#160;</span>&#160;8. <a href="/wiki/Oryol" title="Oryol">Orel</a> (Don) dialect</div>
<div><span style="display:inline-block; width:1.5em; height:1.5em; margin:1px 0; border:1px solid black; background-color:#FF7D26; color:black; font-size:100%; text-align:center;">&#160;</span>&#160;9. <a href="/wiki/Ryazan" title="Ryazan">Ryazan</a> dialect</div>
<div><span style="display:inline-block; width:1.5em; height:1.5em; margin:1px 0; border:1px solid black; background-color:#FFAA71; color:black; font-size:100%; text-align:center;">&#160;</span>&#160;10. <a href="/wiki/Tula,_Russia" title="Tula, Russia">Tula</a> dialect</div>
